d you guys hear her"],[2335,2464,"Spanish and her Chinese?"],[2464,2594,"She sounded native in both."],[2594,2719,"She clearly belongs here."],[2719,2827,"She remembered all that data"],[2827,2936,"right off the top of her head."],[4149,4237,"Learning Chinese?"],[4404,4458,"Ain't gonna help you"],[4458,4554,"with busting tables, bro."],[4683,4796,"Learning is never in vain."],[4850,4988,"I heard Maple Media's hiring"],[4988,5088,"and they want people who know"],[5088,5238,"Chinese, Spanish and English."],[5313,5434,"I thought maybe I could work there."],[5718,5793,"Emma?"],[5872,5955,"Aren't those the quarterly"],[5955,6043,"sales results?"],[6177,6268,"You're just an intern."],[6318,6423,"Why do you need to study this?"],[6498,6560,"I thought it'll help"],[6560,6648,"me do my job better"],[6648,6752,"if I learn as much as I can."]],"54":[[300,387,"You and William"],[387,579,"are from two very different worlds."],[592,713,"A poor country girl"],[713,955,"like you doesn't belong in our worlds."],[1017,1121,"And it'll never work out."],[2239,2344,"Congratulations."],[2381,2489,"Tonight was a big night for you."],[2686,2798,"Congrats to you too, William."],[3620,3674,"It's time."],[3941,4033,"Let's get a divorce."]],"55":[[1906,1960,"Hey."],[2473,2502,"Sir,"],[2540,2656,"should we catch up to Miss Emma?"],[2723,2848,"It's not safe for her to walk"],[2848,2936,"alone at this hour."],[2973,3094,"Why are you so concerned?"],[3094,3199,"Are you in love with her too?"],[3303,3324,"No,"],[3428,3511,"of course not, boss."],[3599,3687,"Wait uh, why..."],[3778,3828,"Are you"],[3899,3953,"in love with her?"],[4012,4079,"Start the car."],[4079,4162,"We're going home."],[4416,4446,"Wait."],[4475,4575,"Turn around and follow her."],[4662,4729,"Yes, sir."],[4988,5030,"Oh,"],[5109,5313,"I am so sorry."],[5313,5413,"Are you all right?"],[5505,5555,"Timmy?"],[5684,5759,"It's Emma."],[5789,5855,"Emma Adams."],[6026,6068,"Emma..."],[6214,6264,"Timmy!"],[6890,7007,"It really is you."],[71